title: Kuttanpillayude Sivarathri
subTitle: When Kuttan Pillai dies during Shivarathri, he returns as a ghost, observing his family's struggles and their conflicts over a cherished tree.

title: Veera Simha Reddy
subTitle: Jai Simha Reddy, the son of the esteemed Veera Simha Reddy, returns home to avenge his father's death as a result of village politics.

title: Bhramam
subTitle: Ray, a pianist, pretends to be a visually impaired man. However, things take a turn for the worse when he unwittingly gets involved in the murder of a former actor.

title: Teja Bhai and Family
subTitle: Teja Bhai, a gangster falls in love with Vedhika, a simple girl. He has to leave his criminal life behind in order to seek her father's consent to marry her.

title: Vinodayathra
subTitle: Vinod, a quarrelsome young man, moves into his sister's house in a village to get his life in order. There, he happens to meet Anupama and falls in love with her.

title: Drishyam 2
subTitle: Georgekutty, a cinema hall owner, is a changed man who thrives in life. However, when his family become entangled in a criminal investigation, he must protect them from the legal institution.

title: Thrissur Pooram
subTitle: Pullu Giri is trying to live a peaceful life and forget his ruffian past. Following an incident, he gets dragged into the affairs of some local gangs.

title: Christian Brothers
subTitle: When the daughter of a minister gets kidnapped, Christy is called upon to rescue her. Although he manages to save her, he himself gets embroiled in the kidnapper's murder.

title: Nadodimannan
subTitle: Padmanabhan, a man who joins political rallies to make money, gets into trouble when he is elected mayor of Thiruvananthapuram and is forced to fight corruption in the city.

title: Nadodimannan
subTitle: Padmanabhan, a man who joins political rallies to make money, gets into trouble when he is elected mayor of Thiruvananthapuram and is forced to fight corruption in the city.

title: I.G.
subTitle: Inspector General Durga Prasad gets appointed as the head of an an anti-terrorism squad. However, a revelation soon forces him to choose between his family and his duty.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: Pulliman
subTitle: Kunjunni, an orphan, and Radha, who makes a living by selling statues of deities, love each other. However, problems arise when her father opposes their relationship.

title: Oru Yamandan Premakadha
subTitle: Lallu, a happy-go-lucky person who loves to hang out with his friends, is in pursuit of true love. One day, he finds a photo of a missing woman, Diya, in the newspaper and feels a spark.

title: Oru Maravathoor Kanavu
subTitle: Michael and his family buy a farm that is coveted by a rich man, who makes life difficult for him. Thereafter, Michael's brother, Chandy, comes to support him.

title: Aadu 2
subTitle: Shaji Pappan and his team participate in a tug-of-war tournament to overcome their financial crisis. However, fate entangles them in a counterfeiting deal.

title: Minnaminnikkoottam
subTitle: Ajit, an anchor in Kolkata, meets Krishnapriya, who has lost her husband under mysterious circumstances. However, things become complicated when he falls for her while helping to find her spouse.

title: Naran
subTitle: Velayudhan, an orphan, is loved by the villagers as he keeps the village free from unsavoury people and practices. However, an evil moneylender and politician get jealous and try to get rid of him.

title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: Aayudham
subTitle: When a powerful explosion occurs at the Vilayam beach seconds after Chief Minister Madhavan leaves the venue, Police Officer Rishikesh is tasked with the investigation to find the truth behind the blast.

title: Rosapoo
subTitle: Shajahan struggles to make ends meet after suffering a huge loss in his duty-free shop. His friend Neeraj, who aspires to become a director, ropes Shajahan into his idea of making an adult film.

title: Malayali
subTitle: Madhavan is loved and respected by everyone in the village except his brothers who hate him. Matters get worse after his brothers try to falsely implicate him in an acquaintance's murder case.

title: Love Action Drama
subTitle: Dinesh, a conceited and wealthy young bachelor, goes to extreme lengths to impress a girl named Shobha with the help of his best friend Sagar, and Dinesh eventually hopes to marry Shobha.

title: Udayananu Tharam
subTitle: A struggling director gets cheated by his friend who steals his script and becomes a famous actor. However, when he finally gets the chance to direct a film, he is forced to cast a dubious actor.

title: Hridayam
subTitle: Arun, a young man, enrols in an engineering college but falls prey to bad habits. As he grows up, he decides to turn over a new leaf and become a responsible adult.

title: Adi Kapyare Koottamani
subTitle: Lakshmi, hoping to enter and exit the college hostel unnoticed, offers Bhanuprasad, a student, a sum of money. However, she ends up trapped in the building due to a series of chaotic events.

title: Premalu
subTitle: Having been rejected once, Sachin, a young man, falls for Reenu, a girl he meets during a wedding, and sets out to win her over.

title: Rappakal
subTitle: Saraswathiyamma is the head of a noble family that treats her servant Krishnan as one of her own sons. When her relatives conspire to sell her house, she and Krishnan set out to save it.
